      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This example remains mechanically robust, with the critical VANOS system serviced and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014essential for maintaining chassis integrity under high-torque loads. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction, complemented by a suspension setup that retains its signature communicative feedback. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the powertrain remains tight, pulling hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with the unmistakable metallic rasp of the factory exhaust. A purist\u2019s spec, mechanically sound and ready for the apex.",
